nodes.text: The Qulun camp was a camp used by the Qulun, a non-traditional trading clan of the Alwari tribes native to the planet Ansion. The Qulun constantly moved around Ansion, setting up camp when they traded.

In 22 BBY, four Jedi—Masters Luminara Unduli and Obi-Wan Kenobi, and their Padawans Barriss Offee and Anakin Skywalker—along with Kyakhta, Bulgan, and Tooqui, while believing themselves to be guests of trader-chief Baiuntu, were in fact his captives and, upon being freed by Tooqui, fought the Qulun in a skirmish in their camp.
